metadata.name: Tomodachi Key
metadata.description:
Tomodachi (友達) means “friend” in Japanese. The tomodachi keys are created to be gifted from Plug-holders to the frens they want to invite to Sugoi. The image is a young girl holding a teddy bear and a key. Her third eye has opened, signifying enlightenment.

The first 888 wallets to mint the contract will have the Vanguard attribute, which differentiates early adopters. The Vanguard attribute will confer priority access to future Sugoi events and drops.
